00:54:15,993 --> 00:54:26,638
I certainly don't disagree that a standard process and procedure that would allow for, you know, the renaming of any municipal facility or building or

706
00:54:27,710 --> 00:54:33,933
I think we might even want to outline everything we mean here because he meant in corners and streets and that kind of thing would be good.

