718
00:55:36,045 --> 00:55:37,405
The school committee is a separate body.

719
00:55:37,425 --> 00:55:38,486
They're an autonomous body.

720
00:55:39,006 --> 00:55:40,947
And I understand the boundaries.

721
00:55:41,667 --> 00:55:44,489
However, we are the legislative body for the entire community.

722
00:55:45,069 --> 00:55:49,271
And the school committee falls under the purview of this city.

723
00:55:49,911 --> 00:55:51,172
And if the

724
00:55:52,171 --> 00:55:59,594
solicitor came back and said, I don't believe that you can do that as a council through way of ordinance, to me, then the issue would be dropped by myself.

725
00:56:00,194 --> 00:56:02,055
I'm not gonna pursue anything.

