727
00:56:15,399 --> 00:56:20,041
But all I'm doing is asking what our options are right now.

728
00:56:20,454 --> 00:56:23,455
and not forcing anything on anyone at this particular point.

729
00:56:23,955 --> 00:56:26,116
So that's all I wanna get across, Mr. President.

730
00:56:29,937 --> 00:56:32,678
Perhaps can we ask two questions instead of one then?

731
00:56:34,158 --> 00:56:41,460
Could the city ask the city solicitor for a ruling on whether the council through ordinance can craft a process for the naming of a school building?

732
00:56:42,020 --> 00:56:46,942
And then maybe the second one could be a further resolve that the city council ask the city solicitor for

733
00:56:48,554 --> 00:56:53,837
an example of a process for the naming of any municipal building or facility, something like that.

734
00:56:53,897 --> 00:56:58,661
