736
00:57:10,208 --> 00:57:14,871
It's not in from what I can read a motion or an attempt to preclude

737
00:57:15,682 --> 00:57:36,256
any elected body from exercising their rights, what it's doing is establishing, requesting more or less an opinion as to whether or not a universal and standardized process can be crafted so that that can be utilized across all realms of government when it comes to the renaming of any type of facility of the like.

738
00:57:36,276 --> 00:57:38,238
I don't really think we need to split hairs over this.

739
00:57:38,318 --> 00:57:40,379
