Do we wait till the papers close?

991
01:19:02,074 --> 01:19:10,635
How much time do we need to get this legislation to get passed before we have to, can we do it after the paper deadline closes, but still have enough time to pass the normal petition?

992
01:19:10,735 --> 01:19:15,216
You know, those are some of the questions that are from an operational standpoint that come up.

993
01:19:15,256 --> 01:19:21,557
